edu.uml.cs.isense.queue
Class QueueLayout

java.lang.Object
  Activity
      edu.uml.cs.isense.queue.QueueLayout

public class QueueLayout
extends Activity

Activity that displays the list of data sets stored in the data saving queue. From here, the user can check and uncheck data sets to upload, rename them, change their data, delete them, or attempt to upload them to iSENSE.

Field Detail

PARENT_NAME

public static final java.lang.String PARENT_NAME
Global string constant that the user should use to pass in the parent name of their activity when using an intent to launch QueueLayout. QueueLayout will not display if a parent name is not passed into it. This parent name is used to create a serializable file with the same name as the string passed to it.
